(motorcycle engines roaring)

3
00:00:04,224 --> 00:00:07,641
(bright music continues)

4
00:00:12,929 --> 00:00:15,512
(upbeat music)

5
00:00:16,443 --> 00:00:19,026
(David laughs)

6
00:00:23,499 --> 00:00:26,916
(upbeat music continues)

7
00:00:28,109 --> 00:00:31,026
